      "message": "This forces the user to pass \"template-prefix\" in the request, its probably how it will be used most of the time, but to keep things flexible it's better to get this value from the nodeTemplate input as we do for ResourceResolution component. Example\n \n            \"ResourceResolutionComponent\" : {\n              \"operations\" : {\n                \"process\" : {\n                  \"inputs\" : {\n                    \"artifact-prefix-names\" : {\n                      \"get_input\": \"template-prefix\"\n                    },",
