      "message": "attributes here, define the components output attributes which then other components can do get_attribute on. In this case your component does not set this attribute, so it should be removed. \n\nYou should consider setting some kind of attribute which could be used for workflow outputs to signal success or failure - like you did for operational output. Could be for example\n\n  \"attributes\": {\n    \"status\": {\n      \"required\": true,\n      \"type\": \"string\"\n    },\n    \"response-data\": {\n      \"required\": false,\n      \"type\": \"json\"\n    }",
      "author": {
